data.description: Location Location! Near Summerlin, The Kellogg Zaher Sports Complex, Angel Park Golf Course, Las Vegas Sports Park, Tivoli Village & Boca Park. A 2 story, 3 bedroom & a loft, with 3 car garage home is awaiting your purchase. Last comparable of the same model sold for $467,000 on 3.23. The very high vaulted ceilings are amazing. The primary bedroom is separated from the other bedrooms with a large loft, which could be a 4th bedroom. The private back yard has turf, a covered patio & matured landscaping. House exterior painted about 1 year ago, & the downstairs interior painted about 2 years ago. Oven, stove & microwave are new. Home is in need of some TLC. Seller is offering a $3,750 incentive, which will be credited at the close of escrow, & will pay off the $15,000 balance for the solar panels at list price. Buy it & make it your own! Owner has an assumable FHA loan @ 4.625%, w/ a balance of $349K. Buyer must qualify & pay the difference between the loan & sales price in cash.
